---
title: Veggie Rigatoni Bolognaise with Aubergine and Olives
description: This super speedy lentil bolognese is perfect for a midweek meal. The combination of Italian-style herbs, aubergine and black olives give the dish the rich flavour of bolognese. Our chefs have also included red wine stock to really amp up the flavour. Quick to make and even quicker to eat, this dish will be a winner with everyone around the table.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/veggie-rigatoni-bolognaise-d20cd9bc-21158e23.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipecards/card/veggie-rigatoni-bolognaise-5ef3471a9b582741bf1786b1-acbd9524.pdf
